text: Medway River may refer to: ;In Australia *Medway River (New South Wales), a river in New South Wales, Australia *Medway River (Tasmania), a river in Tasmania, Australia ;In Canada *Medway River, Nova Scotia, a river in Nova Scotia, Canada *Medway Creek (Ontario), A tributary of the Thames River in Southwest Ontario, Canada. ;In New Zealand *Medway River, New Zealand is a river in South Island of New Zealand ;In the United Kingdom *River Medway is a river in the south-east of England == See also == * Medway (disambiguation) * Midway River
